<HEADLINE>
<P>
DOWNTIME: SNUGGLING UP WITH A GOOD MYSTERY NOVEL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Ilike to sit in the center of my bed, lean against a lot of fluffy pillows 
with my favorite plaid blanket over my legs, and read a good mystery book.I 
make myself some hot cinnamon apple tea and drink it while reading. Spending my 
time in bed is especially relaxing and soothing when it's raining or on a gray, 
hazy day. This helps me unwind and forget the world for a while. Afterward, I 
always feel recharged. 
</P>
<P>
 -- BLANCA VALDEZ 
</P>
<P>
 Montebello 
</P>
</TEXT>
