Disney) $107.1 $3,731 3. "Disclosure" $7.3 1,810 2 (Warner Bros.) $20.9 $4,044 
4. "Drop Zone" $4.0 2,055 2 (Paramount) $12.3 $1,960 5. "Speechless" $3.9 1,404 
