<HEADLINE>
<P>
EXECUTIVE SUITE: SMITH LEAVES DICK CLARK PRODUCTIONS FOR MCA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Arthur Smith is leaving Dick Clark Productions to become senior vice president 
at MCA Television Group. 
</P>
<P>
 Smith had been senior vice president at Clark's production company, which he 
