<P>
 Plasma and Materials Technologies Inc. has named John W. LaValle vice 
president of finance and administration. 
</P>
<P>
 Prior to joining PMT, LaValle was vice president and chief financial officer 
at Superconductor Technologies Inc. in Santa Barbara. 
</P>
<P>
