<HEADLINE>
<P>
REGIONAL EARNINGS: PICO PRODUCTS EARNINGS FOR 1ST QUARTER FALL BY 28% 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Pico Products Inc., a Lake View Terrace manufacturer of pay-TV security 
devices, reported that its fiscal first-quarter earnings fell by 28%.It said 
the decline resulted from its investments in new products and a regional office 
in Hong Kong. 
</P>
<P>
 In the quarter that ended Oct. 31, Pico earned $182,904, while its sales rose 
4% to $8.09 million. A year earlier, the company had net income of $252,478 on 
$7.76 million in sales. 
</P>
</TEXT>
