<P>
 A U.S. federal jury Monday convicted a Colombian drug cartel hit man for the 
1989 bombing that killed 107 people aboard an Avianca Airlines jet.Dandenny 
Munoz-Mosquera, 28, also was convicted on charges of drug trafficking, 
conspiracy and murder. 
