 Davstar Industries 
</P>
<P>
 * Headquarters: Costa Mesa 
</P>
<P>
 * Founded: Aug. 28, 1985 
</P>
<P>
 * Officers of new company: 
</P>
<P>
 Charles A. Laverty, chairman and chief executive officer; Dr. Gerald W. Timm, 
vice chairman and executive vice president; Michael A. Piraino, chief operating 
officer; Kevin Davidson, vice president 
</P>
<P>
 * Employees: About 150 
</P>
<P>
 * Business: Designer and manufacturer of medical products. 
</P>
<P>
