<TEXT>
<P>
 New Year's Events: The Anaheim Hilton is offering three choices to diners in a 
bid to lure New Year's celebrants. 
</P>
<P>
 The biggest bash at the hotel will be in the Hilton's northern Italian-style 
restaurant, Pavia, where a five-course dinner will be served, including a 
