<DATE>
<P>
December 20, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Life & Style; Part E; Page 1; Column 2; View Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
880 words 
</P>
