</P>
<P>
 Ventura County vacancy rates for commercial, industrial and retail businesses 
showed a dramatic decline from the first quarter of 1993 and the fourth quarter 
of 1994. 
</P>
<P>
 The vacancy rate is the percentage of available space that goes unrented or 
unsold. 03,20,12,08 INDUSTRIAL RETAIL OFFICE SPACE SPACE SPACE 1993 1st 
